These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, fantasy
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy | musical |
| Flower   | bellflower       | marigold  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, july
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, r&b
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, sports
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday          | july | may |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | r&b         |
| Movie-Genre           | sports     | adventure         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager
City: new-york, nizza
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Flower         | azalea          | aconite |
| Job           | project-manager | analyst     |
| City   | new-york            | nizza         |
| Transport     | scooter         | quad-bike   |

