.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, parkour
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Sport      | parkour     | handball   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance |
| Game           | mah-jongg | scrabble    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-5::.
City: venice, hamburg
There 2 different types of food: kale, kiwi
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, tennis
1. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating kale##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2       |
| City   | venice        | hamburg        |
| Food       | kale       | kiwi         |
| Hobby        | traveling | rock-climbing |
| Sport      | climbing   | tennis       |

