.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, cooking
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, jazz
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who likes pink is the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of folk is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby      | cooking     | singing |
| Color          | aquamarine   | pink |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | folk     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 